scene.message:
Nanjo: Yes.{nl}
I'm worried about Inaba{nl}
and Sonomura.{waitkey}{clearbox}And there's something{nl}
that troubles me.{waitkey}That student in the white{nl}
mask looked a lot{nl}
like Sonomura...{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Yes!{nl}
I'm worried about{nl}
Mark and Maki.{waitkey}{clearbox}And something troubles{nl}
me too...{waitkey}That person in the white{nl}
mask looked just like Maki.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: We have to find{nl}
Sonomura.{waitkey}She seemed to be{nl}
suffering somehow.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Can't be helped.{nl}
Well, we'll figure it out{nl}
eventually.{waitkey}{ret}

Ms. Saeko: ...I see.{waitkey}{nl}
Then go give it your all,{nl}
with no regrets!{waitkey}{clearbox}You're all adults now.{nl}
I won't stop adults from{nl}
leaving the nest by choice.{waitkey}{clearbox}But in exchange{wait_fr:30}...{wait_fr:30}...{waitkey}{ret}

Ms. Saeko: Come back before{nl}
you turn into old men!{waitkey}{clearbox}And report to me in person{nl}
that everyone's safe!{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Yeah,{nl}
no need to worry!{waitkey}{clearbox}After all, we're{nl}
Ms. Saeko's{nl}
star pupils!{waitkey}{ret}

Ms. Saeko: Star pupils indeed.{waitkey}{nl}
Every last one of you{nl}
dressed against the rules!{waitkey}{clearbox}Once in a while, try{nl}
putting yourself in your{nl}
homeroom teacher's shoes!!{waitkey}{clearbox}Day after day,{nl}
the vice principal chews{nl}
me out...{waitkey}{ret}

Ms. Saeko: Heh...{nl}
Though it seems even the{nl}
vice principal had a change{nl}
of heart over all this.{waitkey}{clearbox}He asked me to tell{nl}
you all "thank you."{waitkey}{clearbox}For a while he might even{nl}
turn a blind eye to your{nl}
dress code violations.{waitkey}{ret}

Ms. Saeko: He's got his{nl}
good points, you know.{waitkey}{clearbox}Now! This is no time{nl}
to stand around{nl}
chatting!!{waitkey}{clearbox}If you don't get going soon,{nl}
the sun'll set!!{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Well, you've got me{nl}
along, so there's{nl}
nothing to worry about.{waitkey}{clearbox}...{wait_fr:15}...{wait_fr:15}Whoops!{nl}
Tears don't suit a pretty{nl}
face, now.{wait_fr:30} Honey{color:3}♥{color:0}{waitkey}Dehyahyahyahyahyahya{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: And so the school{nl}
returns to normal...{waitkey}{clearbox}But this is only{nl}
the beginning, isn't it.{waitkey}{clearbox}Take back the town,{nl}
take back our peaceful days,{nl}
the real battle comes after.{waitkey}{clearbox}To fight through this long,{nl}
long life{wait_fr:30} Do my best!{waitkey}I'll give it my all,{nl}
with no regrets.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Where there's a will,{nl}
there's a way{wait_fr:30}, hm.{waitkey}With this lot around,{nl}
I'm starting to truly{nl}
believe it.{waitkey}{clearbox}Ms. Saeko!{nl}
We'll find Inaba and{nl}
Sonomura without fail!{waitkey}{clearbox}{ctl0f:1}!{nl}
Let's go!!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Up till now I've{nl}
just sort of drifted{nl}
through life, but{waitkey}{clearbox}Watching {ctl0f:1} and{nl}
Mayuzumi push themselves so{nl}
hard made me feel I{nl}
should try harder too.{waitkey}{clearbox}As for what to work toward,{nl}
I'll decide that after we{nl}
fix the town for now.{waitkey}{clearbox}See ya, teach!{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Once the town's back{nl}
to normal, I'll study{nl}
for real.{waitkey}{clearbox}I'll study{wait_fr:30}{nl}
and someday become a fine{nl}
teacher like you, Ms. Saeko!{waitkey}{clearbox}Heh...{wait_fr:30}{nl}
I won't say goodbye,{wait_fr:30} teach!{waitkey}{ret}

Ms. Saeko: {ctl0f:1}!{nl}
Thank you for everything.{waitkey}{clearbox}Everyone seems to have{nl}
found something to think{nl}
about for their future.{waitkey}What about you?{waitkey}{ret}

Ms. Saeko: That's the spirit!{waitkey}{clearbox}Don't forget how you feel{nl}
now that you've accomplished{nl}
something great, and{nl}
give it your all!!{waitkey}{ret}

Ms. Saeko: I see.{waitkey}{nl}
Well, you're young,{nl}
so no need to rush.{waitkey}In any case, I'm counting{nl}
on you to look after{nl}
everyone!{waitkey}{ret}

Ms. Saeko: Oh my,{nl}
where did you slip in from?{waitkey}{clearbox}Heh...{nl}
You celebrate these kids'{nl}
send-off too, won't you.{waitkey}{ret}
